:::
:::               Examples:
:::                  lpad(15,'0000')    returns "0015"
:::                  lpad(15,'    ')    returns "  15"
:::                  lpad(19011,'0000') returns "19011"
:::
:::      input  - The TextStream object from which input is read.
:::               This may be stdin or a file.
:::
